sources.title: What's Up Front (1963) MARYILN MANNING
sources.description:
♣ 1st TIME on YouTUBE ♣
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX
Writer/Producer: Arch Hall Sr.
Director: Bob Wehling
Starring: Tommy Holden, Marilyn Manning, Carolyn Walker, Arch Hall Sr.

In this Campy Comedy, a zealous salesman saves his company from going bankrupt by selling its products door-to-door.

TRIVIA: Marilyn Manning is best remembered for the two Cult films she made with co-star Arch Hall Jr., Eegah! and The Sadist.

metadata.Plot: A small-town boy saves a brassiere company from going bankrupt by becoming the world's greatest door-to-door bra salesman.
metadata.Actors: Tommy Holden, Marilyn Manning, Carolyn Walker
